{"tid":189481,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"Canon定焦鏡選擇","createTime":"2017-04-06T12:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T06:38:14.000Z","uid":19900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0ee6f262b9c578f2ed002073fff0d6830dd65d3","tid":189481,"uid":19900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:44:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.dcfever.com/lens/specification.php?id=79\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Flens%2Fspecification.php%3Fid%3D79&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=79dac586\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dcfever.com/lens/specification.php?id=79</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dcfever.com/lens/specification.php?id=230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Flens%2Fspecification.php%3Fid%3D230&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=2da1c7ca\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dcfever.com/lens/specification.php?id=230</a><br />\n<br />\n考慮緊兩支定焦鏡，想問有無用家俾d意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSigma睇過一般都話唔錯，但紫邊問題都有唔少人講嚴重，但1.4光圈真係好吸引<br />\n<br />\nCanon其實評價好好，但因為自己用開2.8光圈覺唔夠用，所以想要大d嘅光圈，但佢得2.0，唔知個分別明唔明顯"},{"pid":"6eeb2cd81bac9e1043f6f001cfae30af78f33c1f","tid":189481,"uid":19900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:51:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://blog.yam.com/xingye/article/35611122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.yam.com%2Fxingye%2Farticle%2F35611122&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=9e115f05\" target=\"_blank\">http://blog.yam.com/xingye/article/35611122</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mobile01.com/topicdetail.php?f=253&amp;t=431203\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobile01.com%2Ftopicdetail.php%3Ff%3D253%26t%3D431203&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=4f783d49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mobile01.com/topicdetail.php?f=253&amp;t=431203</a>"},{"pid":"541c1ab4620de9eca524ce9552cc7aad5c568d60","tid":189481,"uid":7378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:34:15.000Z","msg":"你肯定呢2支鏡仲有貨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 停產好耐"},{"pid":"8dd96555a9f3d535138044038dec1d2a0f6089db","tid":189481,"uid":98748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T17:54:56.000Z","msg":"師兄用緊咩機？<br />\n<br />\n我用緊Canon 50mm f1.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n價錢平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e6b76871603276ed73dfce37a69f5df14d2306","tid":189481,"uid":11916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T17:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g2y4042.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg2y4042.jpg&h=261d0d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n35mm1.8"},{"pid":"b1a46e2fa4e8403b29319d854e8e894e9f8c2cd9","tid":189481,"uid":19900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T19:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>師兄用緊咩機？<br />\n<br />\n我用緊Canon 50mm f1.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n價錢平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCanon 700d<br />\n50mm呢支試過 覺得太近 空間細d都影唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純影企定定嘅model係唔錯嘅"},{"pid":"e5808c7eb536c606004081affb71e1b65aa6391b","tid":189481,"uid":19900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T19:59:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g2y4042.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg2y4042.jpg&h=261d0d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n35mm1.8</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTamron我未見過有呢支啵<br />\n多數係sigma 師兄覺得效果如何？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10656718ac746d57e41dbb8dbe6d4c890db0983a","tid":189481,"u